legal:DuocNguoiSuDungLaoDongChuyenSangLamCongViecNheHonAnToanHonMaKhongBiCatGiamTienLuongVaQuyenLoiIchChoDenHetThoiGianNuoiConDuoi12ThangTuoi rdf:type legal:LegalEntity .
