legal:LaoDongNuLamNgheCongViecNangNhocDocHaiNguyHiemHoacDacBietNangNhocDocHaiNguyHiemHoacLamNgheCongViecCoAnhHuongXauToiChucNangSinhSanVaNuoiConKhiMangThaiVaCoThongBaoChoNguoiSuDungLaoDongBiet legal:choPhep legal:DuocNguoiSuDungLaoDongChuyenSangLamCongViecNheHonAnToanHonMaKhongBiCatGiamTienLuongVaQuyenLoiIchChoDenHetThoiGianNuoiConDuoi12ThangTuoi .
